              <h4 class="h6 fw-bold mb-1">birdnet (Python Package)</h4>
              <p class="smaller text-muted mb-0">Native Python integration for developers and data scientists. Build custom pipelines or run large-scale inference on your own infrastructure. <a href="https://birdnet-team.github.io/birdnet/" target="_blank">Documentation →</a></p>
