              <p class="smaller text-muted mb-0">User-friendly utilities for researchers. Access graphical interfaces for managing thousands of detections, verifying species, and preparing data for publication. <a href="https://birdnet-team.github.io/BirdNET-Analyzer/" target="_blank">Documentation →</a></p>
            </div>
          </div>
